Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.80,0:00:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and Sanji who had parted ways\Nfinally reunited at the rendezvous.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.08,0:00:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.46,0:00:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna crash Big Mom's tea party\Nand the wedding
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.73,0:00:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and save Sanji's family!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.38,0:00:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Sanji'll be back with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.79,0:00:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B... Big...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.96,0:00:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy... She's the Emperor of the Sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.00,0:00:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And then, Jimbei suggested a plan to Luffy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.90,0:00:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know Capone "Gang" Bege, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.87,0:00:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he's the one who took Sanji away.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.83,0:00:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The main event of the tea party is\Nthe wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.66,0:00:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you already know, Big Mom intends to\Nkill all the members of the Vinsmokes at the wedding
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.63,0:01:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and acquire all of Germa.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.51,0:01:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bege is going to kill Big Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.55,0:01:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.08,0:01:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?\NSeems like everyone has their own plot!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.31,0:01:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel bad for Pekoms\Nbut under the circumstances,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.19,0:01:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}do you really want to\Nmake an enemy of Bege?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.92,0:01:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.68,0:01:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's join Bege!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.18,0:01:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.10,0:01:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"A Secret Meeting!\NLuffy vs. the Fire Tank Pirates!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.80,0:02:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.40,0:02:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.22,0:02:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you crazy, Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.20,0:02:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You actually like it, Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.22,0:02:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, I told you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.80,0:02:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, four out of six of us are against it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.04,0:02:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you hear about Bege-{\i1}san{\i0}'s ill deeds?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.14,0:02:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that way, everything'll \Nwork out, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.24,0:02:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't make a decision like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.28,0:02:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Actually, I've already made an arrangement.\NDo you want to meet him?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.48,0:02:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's see him now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.10,0:02:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.23,0:02:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.\NYou can say no if it feels off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.19,0:02:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our goal is slightly different from theirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.34,0:02:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy, Sanji. Bege and his clan's base is\Nin the northwest of the island.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.78,0:02:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The eight of us will head there first\Nfrom this dimension. See you there!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.26,0:02:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Stop counting us in!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.54,0:03:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.07,0:03:10.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,FIRE TANK PIRATES' BASE\NNORTHWEST WHOLE CAKE ISLAND
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.78,0:03:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you kill Bobbin?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.14,0:03:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he was going after Black-Leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.29,0:03:16.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,FIRE TANK PIRATES
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.52,0:03:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, Germa are my heroes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.63,0:03:23.38,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,"PHANTOM GUN" VITO
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.40,0:03:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they really coming here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.33,0:03:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.63,0:03:30.91,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,"HIT MAN" GOTTI
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.93,0:03:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jimbei isn't the type of man to joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.43,0:03:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we're both standing against Big Mom,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.75,0:03:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we shouldn't make extra enemies -\Nhe's right about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.09,0:03:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now it depends on what Straw Hat will say.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.47,0:03:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't like it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.78,0:04:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just kill him!
