Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.37,0:08:05.20,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,EASTERN INLET
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.22,0:08:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Pekoms! You still have to rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.75,0:08:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grr! Has Jimbei really told Mama\Nabout that damn rat Bege?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.42,0:08:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.86,0:08:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By now, I'm guessing that the traitor Bege\Nhas been beaten relentlessly by Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.74,0:08:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grr! You guess?! Your guess isn't enough!\NI gotta make sure to tell her...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.65,0:08:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa-whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.23,0:08:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to keep resting, Pekoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.97,0:08:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Praline,\Nin case they stop him from telling her... Grr!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.68,0:08:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's your concern,\Nit's even better for you to leave it to Jimbei!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.81,0:08:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be beaten again in your condition now.\NJust keep quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.58,0:08:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right, Pekoms!\NAs a ship's doctor, I won't allow you to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.88,0:08:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ever get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.61,0:09:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right! He's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.19,0:09:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yeah.\N--Rest! Rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.65,0:09:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are acting weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.79,0:09:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gulp!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.34,0:09:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was something going on\Nall through the night in the inlet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.51,0:09:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw some people carrying things around!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.49,0:09:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gulp!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.31,0:09:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We can't let Pekoms know that\NJimbei is trying to be part of...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.98,0:09:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...the Big Mom assassination plot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.02,0:09:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate that you saved me\Nbut I gotta go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.40,0:09:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, we can't allow that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.70,0:09:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that? Grr!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.57,0:09:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys hiding?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.89,0:09:49.06,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,GULP!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.08,0:09:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gulp!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.76,0:10:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.12,0:10:11.29,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,FIRE TANK PIRATES' BASE
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.31,0:10:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Bege's base!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.82,0:10:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what kind of guy is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.78,0:10:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You heard what Jimbei said.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.62,0:10:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.17,0:10:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think of him as a scheming\Nand brutal mafia boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.69,0:11:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My hero! Vinsmoke Sanji of Germa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.94,0:11:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy to see you again-{\i1}rero{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.36,0:11:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.74,0:11:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where's everyone else?\NAre you Bege?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.78,0:11:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be in such a rush.\NThey are here or {\i1}rero{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.29,0:11:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by "{\i1}rero{\i0}"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.04,0:11:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Luffy! Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.29,0:11:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.50,0:11:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You made me worried, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.38,0:11:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for that... Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.18,0:11:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That aside,\Nwhy do you look like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.55,0:11:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you guys go take a bath too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.98,0:11:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you relaxing?! We don't have time!\NAnd you don't even like to bathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.73,0:11:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you two must take one too-{\i1}rero{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.11,0:11:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, we'll talk-{\i1}rero{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.99,0:11:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bath under these circumstances?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.11,0:11:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father doesn't see anyone who is dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.41,0:12:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's dirty?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.12,0:12:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!\NLola was turned into a warthog zombie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.16,0:12:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And she was chasing around\Nthe guy who she fell in love with!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.37,0:12:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds like her!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.92,0:12:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At that time and again\Nin the forest of monsters,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.13,0:12:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what would've happened to me\Nif it weren't for Lola.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.68,0:12:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! But you guys saved my sister too!\NThank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.24,0:12:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm crying tears of joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.85,0:13:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have been very close since we were kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.06,0:13:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because we're twins!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.02,0:13:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A zombie! I can't imagine a dead person moving.\NThe sea is like a wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.86,0:13:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, Lola has turned back to a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.03,0:13:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'm sure she's still \Ndoing well as a pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.00,0:13:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if she found someone to marry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.34,0:13:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Mom sounded so mad when she talked about\NLola running away from a marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.14,0:13:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... that was a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.56,0:13:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.77,0:13:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama is reviled by all Giants \Nin the world for a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.65,0:13:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All Giants in the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.86,0:13:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why even though\NTotto Land has a diverse population,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.66,0:13:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there are no Giants.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.33,0:14:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Giants really exist!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.83,0:14:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One day,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.37,0:14:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a man showed up saying he \Nhad fallen in love with Lola
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.17,0:14:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at first sight and wanted to marry her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.76,0:14:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, believe it or not, he was\NLoki the prince of Elbaph, the Giants' country!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.43,0:14:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A prince?! Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.31,0:14:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama became so happy and teary-eyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.74,0:14:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She thought if Lola became \Nthe princess of Elbaph,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.58,0:14:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,her long-standing feud with \Nthe Giants would be resolved
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.07,0:14:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and she'd even get access to their army\Nwhich is said to be the world's strongest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.24,0:14:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.20,0:14:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.05,0:14:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After that, everything went wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.92,0:14:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She tried to use me as a substitute,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.38,0:14:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he noticed that I wasn't Lola.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.03,0:14:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And her relationship with the Giants\Ngot even worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.10,0:15:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, she gave up the idea of\Nbecoming friendly with actual Giants
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.43,0:15:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and started investing in research\Nto turn people into giants.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.50,0:15:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her anger towards Lola only amplified\Nand she was branded a criminal in this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.45,0:15:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she comes back, she'll get killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.70,0:15:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, she couldn't stand looking at me\Nbecause I look exactly like Lola...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.95,0:15:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get that damn face out of my sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.55,0:15:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time I saw her, she hit me without mercy.\NSo, for years, I always had fresh wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.82,0:15:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd be killed by my own mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.06,0:15:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see that monster \Nas my mother anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.10,0:15:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But since Lola is a happy-go-lucky girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.36,0:16:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess she'd never imagine\Nthat her mother wants to kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.20,0:16:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... Everything makes sense now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.58,0:16:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So when Bege said he was going to kill Mama,\NI felt nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.90,0:16:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You might think I'm terrible\Nbut that's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.67,0:16:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well, the bath felt so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.55,0:16:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, just like heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.97,0:16:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I refuse to move on to the next life!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.47,0:16:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feels like we finished fighting.\NI can't get loose. We still have to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.65,0:16:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-{\i1}san{\i0}, Luffy-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.61,0:16:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found milk in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.16,0:16:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't go into our fridge without asking!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.78,0:16:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly what I needed.\NMy tooth has cracked.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.25,0:16:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got my face broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.88,0:17:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the milk!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.02,0:17:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, all healed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.35,0:17:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is that possible?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.11,0:17:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys.\NHave you really washed yourselves-{\i1}rero{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.28,0:17:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, totally!\NLet us see Bege already!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.95,0:17:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet-{\i1}rero{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.54,0:17:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, how cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.29,0:17:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we wear these?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.76,0:17:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do I look?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.60,0:17:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're looking great, Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.97,0:17:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do {\i1}I{\i0} look?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.10,0:17:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look nice too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.85,0:18:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look what I found!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.07,0:18:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! That's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.03,0:18:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.62,0:18:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the robot from Germa's comic strip.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.29,0:18:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do they have that here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.92,0:18:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe, there's a big fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.88,0:18:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.34,0:18:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.50,0:19:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is your last chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.80,0:19:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.17,0:19:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you come back with us,\NI'll drive you like a horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.14,0:19:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be prepared!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.23,0:19:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.10,0:19:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean you'll never let me go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.69,0:19:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're {\i1}extremely{\i0} sexy after a bath too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.61,0:19:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive you, Chiffon?!\NI can't believe you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.95,0:19:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you help someone\Nwho wants to kill Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.02,0:19:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiffon-{\i1}sama{\i0}, please think twice!\NYou know no one can ever kill Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.33,0:19:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sis Brulee!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.91,0:19:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know what she has done to me, don't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.67,0:19:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lola is in danger\Nand Bege and Pez are my only family!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.39,0:19:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need anyone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.64,0:20:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's okay, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.19,0:20:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.15,0:20:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.17,0:21:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you Bege?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.72,0:21:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.85,0:21:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.93,0:21:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think so?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.89,0:21:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, which one of you is Bege?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.98,0:21:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, wait. He'll be here soon-{\i1}rero{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.19,0:21:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, everyone's here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.57,0:21:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a bit cleaner now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.49,0:21:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's said "Clothes make the man."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.87,0:21:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't do business with anyone\Nwho doesn't care about their appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.54,0:21:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, we have three and a half hours to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.72,0:21:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.63,0:22:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, whether or not we join forces...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.67,0:22:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Minister is here! Open the gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.51,0:22:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.71,0:22:55.91,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,CHARLOTTE OVEN\NMINISTER OF BAKING (FOURTH SON OF CHARLOTTE)\NBIG MOM PIRATES
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.93,0:22:56.09,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,BIG MOM'S TEA PARTY STARTS\NIN THREE AND A HALF HOURS
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.11,0:23:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Big Mom's tea party starts\Nin three and a half hours.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.92,0:23:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy vs. Bege!\NThe chaotic meeting finally starts!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.59,0:23:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's only one weak point for them\Nto take down the invincible Big Mom.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.10,0:23:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is the secret weapon that holds the key\Nto fulfill the mission?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.29,0:23:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An unprecedented pirate alliance is formed!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.60,0:23:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!\N"The Deadly Pact! Luffy & Bege's Allied Forces!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.36,0:23:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the King of the Pirates!
